data: just imagine, it was moby, so I went to say hello to him, and he told me would you give me a hand with my decks, so I went, and when we finished he gave me a T - shirt and a gold pass to see the concert from the first row, oh my god Kim that the best thing that ever happened to me, well Kim I hope to recieve a letter from you soon, and please tell everybody about the moby concert and everything, thank you.
